  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}No means no.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="SEL_004_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}What's wrong?]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}No what?]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}I am currently negotiating with Koromaru-san.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}Koromaru-san is prohibited from going out for a walk on his own.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}It is time for Koromaru-san's solo patrol duty.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}Commonly known as a "walk."[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}There were arrangements for Sanada-san to accompany Koromaru-san on his walk today.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}However, the scheduled time has passed, and Sanada-san has yet to return.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Koromaru-san's patience has reached its limit.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 9 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 12 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 9 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Arf![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}Koromaru-san is requesting that {f 4 2}-san accompany him, instead.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Are you available to assist at the moment, {f 4 2}-san?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="SEL_011_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I am. Perfect timing.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}What about you, Aigis?]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}You are what they call a "lifesaver."[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}My current mission is to remain on standby at the dormitory.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}I'm afraid I'm fully occupied at the moment.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}I must also request your assistance, {f 4 2}-san.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 9 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}Arf! Arf![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MND_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Koromaru and I left the[n]dorm to go for a walk.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
